  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend the last city of mankind against the endless hordes of darkness</h2>Actively choose when to dodge and heavy attack while slaying 100s of on screen foes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/7230effc3e7876d2c5dbe48c2f9a5f75.poster.avif?t=1677265165\" width=502 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/7230effc3e7876d2c5dbe48c2f9a5f75.webm?t=1677265165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/7230effc3e7876d2c5dbe48c2f9a5f75.mp4?t=1677265165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover the perfect build</h2>Awaken lost heroes with 1000s of potential weapon and ability combinations. Every newly-unlocked hero expands the total ability pool of upgrades that can be earned during a run.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/ba2886aab72901ee2a5d900b50af2008.poster.avif?t=1677265165\" width=504 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/ba2886aab72901ee2a5d900b50af2008.webm?t=1677265165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/ba2886aab72901ee2a5d900b50af2008.mp4?t=1677265165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become the Ultra Blade</h2>Level up and combine weapons to create devastating builds: Two-handed swords that generate explosive earthquakes, spiked bows that shoot ice-infused lasers, the possibilities are almost endless.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/1c319af28972827b78946532dddd8d52.poster.avif?t=1677265165\" width=500 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/1c319af28972827b78946532dddd8d52.webm?t=1677265165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/1c319af28972827b78946532dddd8d52.mp4?t=1677265165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rise to the Challenge</h2>Take on dozens of challenge gauntlets that test your skills and character builds in unique and interesting ways.<br><br><br>Core features include:<br>-12 bespoke characters to unlock<br>-5 core class type (Greatblade, Bow, Gun, Staff, and Shield)<br>-100s of weapons and abilities to master<br>-1000s of potential character + weapon build combinations<br>-Endless Crusade mode that refreshes hourly<br>-27 Challenge gauntlets<br>-15 meta-altering relics to unlock<br>-Simple controls that work with just the arrow keys, a single controller joystick , or just the mouse.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend the last city of mankind against the endless hordes of darkness</h2>Actively choose when to dodge and heavy attack while slaying 100s of on screen foes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/7230effc3e7876d2c5dbe48c2f9a5f75.poster.avif?t=1677265165\" width=502 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/7230effc3e7876d2c5dbe48c2f9a5f75.webm?t=1677265165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/7230effc3e7876d2c5dbe48c2f9a5f75.mp4?t=1677265165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover the perfect build</h2>Awaken lost heroes with 1000s of potential weapon and ability combinations. Every newly-unlocked hero expands the total ability pool of upgrades that can be earned during a run.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/ba2886aab72901ee2a5d900b50af2008.poster.avif?t=1677265165\" width=504 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/ba2886aab72901ee2a5d900b50af2008.webm?t=1677265165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/ba2886aab72901ee2a5d900b50af2008.mp4?t=1677265165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become the Ultra Blade</h2>Level up and combine weapons to create devastating builds: Two-handed swords that generate explosive earthquakes, spiked bows that shoot ice-infused lasers, the possibilities are almost endless.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/1c319af28972827b78946532dddd8d52.poster.avif?t=1677265165\" width=500 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/1c319af28972827b78946532dddd8d52.webm?t=1677265165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165420/extras/1c319af28972827b78946532dddd8d52.mp4?t=1677265165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rise to the Challenge</h2>Take on dozens of challenge gauntlets that test your skills and character builds in unique and interesting ways.<br><br><br>Core features include:<br>-12 bespoke characters to unlock<br>-5 core class type (Greatblade, Bow, Gun, Staff, and Shield)<br>-100s of weapons and abilities to master<br>-1000s of potential character + weapon build combinations<br>-Endless Crusade mode that refreshes hourly<br>-27 Challenge gauntlets<br>-15 meta-altering relics to unlock<br>-Simple controls that work with just the arrow keys, a single controller joystick , or just the mouse.",
